Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.79,0:02:39.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}To take back Sanji who was being pressed into a marriage\Nand left his friends behind,{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.13,0:02:44.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Luffy and the others infiltrated the Whole Cake Island\Nwhere Emperor Big Mom is.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.84,0:02:52.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Pudding whispered a few words to Luffy and Nami\Nwho were held captive by the Big Mom Pirates.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.22,0:02:58.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Meanwhile, in order to obtain the Road Ponegliff,\NPedro invaded the Whole Cake Chateau,{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.40,0:03:02.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}but Baron Tamago stood in his way.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.07,0:03:08.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}They saw each other\Nfor the first time in five years.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.74,0:03:15.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.37,0:03:18.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...expecting to go home alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.54,0:03:26.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}In the world of mirrors, Chopper and Carrot\Nstarted their operation to find Sanji.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.55,0:03:36.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}"The History of the Left Eye!\NPedro vs. Baron Tamago!"{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.56,0:03:42.34,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,SWEET CITY
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.36,0:03:45.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sanji!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.48,0:03:48.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not here!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.65,0:03:50.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sanji!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.07,0:03:55.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, there's a ghost!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.29,0:04:03.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not here either.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.50,0:04:12.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, my!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.14,0:04:20.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it farther away?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.48,0:04:23.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wake up, Brulee!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.36,0:04:27.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where is the mirror to the Whole Cake Chateau?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.44,0:04:34.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We saw it once before.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.12,0:04:36.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.08,0:04:38.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Diesel! Don't you know?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.62,0:04:41.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How do I know? Dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.67,0:04:45.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if Luffy and Nami found Sanji.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.09,0:04:47.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hope so.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.63,0:04:51.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They said they'd go to Mom's castle, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.22,0:04:52.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.09,0:04:58.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As long as we're touching Brulee,\Nwe can jump in and out of the mirrors!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.60,0:05:02.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This dimension is connected to\Nthe mirrors across the Whole Cake Island.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.98,0:05:05.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We should've reached the castle already.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.52,0:05:08.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Brulee! Wake up!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.94,0:05:10.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gee!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.15,0:05:14.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, we gotta try to find it ourselves\Nuntil she wakes up!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.32,0:05:19.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's keep going until we find it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.16,0:05:27.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys will pay for this!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.18,0:05:36.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it, Luffy! What are you thinking?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.51,0:05:43.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's no use.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.56,0:05:46.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't stop,\Nyour hands are gonna tear apart!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.56,0:05:48.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's what I'm trying to do!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.52,0:05:56.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.78,0:05:59.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No! Don't do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.91,0:06:01.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have no choice!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.50,0:06:05.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is there any other way to get us out of here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.88,0:06:10.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it better to have your arms being torn apart...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.05,0:06:12.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...than die?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.84,0:06:15.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A little more to go!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.38,0:06:23.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, no, no!\NThey're really gonna break apart!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.03,0:06:45.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I told you it's no use-{\i1}fa{\i}.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.16,0:06:47.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.83,0:06:52.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.84,0:06:56.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you still trying? Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.30,0:07:04.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not gonna stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.41,0:07:29.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I should tell...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.42,0:07:34.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Big Sister-{\i1}sama{\i}!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.84,0:07:41.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's terrible!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.51,0:07:47.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing up there?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.14,0:07:53.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As you can see,\NI'm trying to get a copy of the Road Ponegliff.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.98,0:07:56.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're very honest.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.57,0:08:00.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But you have nowhere to run.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.45,0:08:08.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Give up and come down here!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.98,0:08:32.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You look so relaxed.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.81,0:08:40.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When you face the Emperor, you have no choice\Nbut to turn defiant instead of being nervous.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.62,0:08:47.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, do you want to fight me?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.91,0:08:52.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, because I haven't fulfilled my mission yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.71,0:08:54.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your mission?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.63,0:08:57.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna take you down
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.30,0:09:05.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and get a copy of the stone!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.32,0:09:22.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You think I can be beaten so easily?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.36,0:09:28.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way. I'm putting my life on the line!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.24,0:09:36.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see. Do whatever you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.75,0:09:40.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Zeus!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.51,0:09:44.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, Mama!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.34,0:09:48.41,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,ZEUS, A THUNDERCLOUD
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.43,0:09:50.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Prometheus!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.22,0:09:54.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, Mama!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.90,0:09:58.50,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,PROMETHEUS, A SUN
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.52,0:10:00.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Napoleon!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.23,0:10:03.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, Mama!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.65,0:10:11.65,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,NAPOLEON, A BICORNE
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.71,0:10:19.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll be mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.96,0:10:27.96,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,COURTYARD ON THE THIRD FLOOR\NWHOLE CAKE CHATEAU
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.10,0:10:37.10,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,PEDRO\NFORMER CAPTAIN OF THE NOX PIRATES\NBOUNTY: 382 MILLION BERRIES
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.81,0:10:45.81,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,BARON TAMAGO\NKNIGHT OF THE BIG MOM PIRATES\NBOUNTY: 429 MILLION BERRIES
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.20,0:10:51.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Straw Hat and Cat Burglar are\Nalready ours-{\i1}bon{\i}.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.95,0:10:54.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Give up-{\i1}bon{\i}.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.96,0:10:57.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So what?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.38,0:11:05.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, let's have it out-{\i1}bon{\i}!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.61,0:11:32.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your Electro won't work against me\Nanymore-{\i1}s'il vous plaît{\i}!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.13,0:11:47.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not going to be scared of the Minks-{\i1}bon{\i}!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.34,0:11:49.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess you're prepared.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.09,0:11:57.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right. I'm wearing special tights\Nthat protect me from Electro-{\i1}feuille{\i}.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.94,0:12:01.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna sort things out with you here!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.98,0:12:08.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For the sake of my dead friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.20,0:12:14.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That must be the Whole Cake Chateau.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.08,0:12:17.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The sweet smell drives me crazy.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.58,0:12:21.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's literally a candy country.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.63,0:12:24.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are we gonna do now, Pedro?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.59,0:12:29.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're talking about Big Mom.\NIt's not gonna be easy, Zepo.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.47,0:12:32.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Big Brothers?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.26,0:12:34.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Big Brothers! I thought so!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.35,0:12:36.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--You-{\i1}gara{\i}...\N--Pekoms.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.35,0:12:38.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Big Brother Pedro! Big Brother Zepo!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.77,0:12:40.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Garchu!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.14,0:12:41.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Garchu...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.90,0:12:43.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Garchu!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.31,0:12:44.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Garchu...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.57,0:12:46.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.11,0:12:50.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Grr! I'm a member of the Big Mom Pirates now.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.66,0:12:53.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Big Mom Pirates?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.91,0:12:59.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are {\i1}you two{\i} doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.37,0:13:07.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's better you don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.51,0:13:14.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We cornered them!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.51,0:13:20.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We've been ambushed?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.52,0:13:24.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't go any farther-{\i1}bon{\i},\NPonegliff thieves!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.23,0:13:31.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not going to let anyone\Nenter the Treasure Repository-{\i1}bon{\i}!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.15,0:13:39.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll never pass through here-{\i1}feuille{\i}!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.20,0:13:47.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're gonna get in there\Nor our trip to this island will be wasted!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.54,0:14:30.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Baron Tamago-{\i1}sama{\i}!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.88,0:14:33.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay, Pedro?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.13,0:14:38.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am but not him.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.85,0:14:46.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn you!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.99,0:15:04.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Big Mom...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.92,0:15:13.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're an exception!\NI have to bring you down myself-{\i1}s'il vous plaît{\i}!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.01,0:15:22.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll lose more than an eye this time!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.95,0:15:45.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.51,0:16:06.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was close-{\i1}bon{\i}!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.98,0:16:10.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My left eye still itches sometimes-{\i1}feuille{\i}.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.56,0:16:14.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I remember the pain of\Ngetting stabbed by you-{\i1}toilette{\i}!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.94,0:16:17.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I remember too, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.86,0:16:25.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened that day\Nremains etched into my left eye!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.80,0:16:41.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look what you've done, you thieves.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.47,0:16:45.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Big Brothers, why?! Grr!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.39,0:16:48.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You tried to steal something on my island
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.89,0:16:52.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and you stabbed Tamago's eyeball.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.31,0:16:57.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have to pay.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.07,0:17:02.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bring the roulette!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.32,0:17:10.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You spin it first.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.34,0:17:17.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.21,0:17:25.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Big Bro!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.73,0:17:37.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm taking 100 years of your life!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.61,0:17:45.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stay with me, Zepo!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.99,0:17:47.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Zepo...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.45,0:17:52.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Zepo!!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.33,0:17:54.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Big Brother Zepo!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.29,0:17:59.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There wasn't enough for 100 years.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.09,0:18:05.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He only had 30 years to live.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.80,0:18:13.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Since you're his partner,\NI need you to pay the rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.40,0:18:23.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, give me the remaining 70 years.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.66,0:18:38.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sunny-side Legs!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.68,0:18:54.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is it-{\i1}bon{\i}!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.69,0:19:08.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're getting tired-{\i1}bon{\i}!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.20,0:19:13.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, give me 70-years' worth of your soul!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.00,0:19:17.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please, Mama!\NHe was like a big brother to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.83,0:19:21.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you take 70 years,\NBig Bro Pedro will die too!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.96,0:19:25.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop, Pekoms. That's pathetic-{\i1}bon{\i}.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.13,0:19:27.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm begging you, Mama!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.26,0:19:31.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pekoms...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.10,0:19:35.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop crying, Pekoms! All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.43,0:19:39.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,10 years. I'll take off 10 years.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.31,0:19:41.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.98,0:19:47.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But you took away an eye from Tamago\Nand that's serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.99,0:19:55.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll take 60 years of your life!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.66,0:20:00.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't you satisfied, Pekoms?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.63,0:20:08.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.85,0:20:18.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Big Mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.44,0:20:22.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How many years will you spare for this?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.52,0:20:27.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Big Bro!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.24,0:20:32.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's pointless to die here!\NThe dawn of the new world is coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.03,0:20:40.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to go back!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.13,0:20:44.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're so handsome.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.55,0:20:47.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll reduce it to 50 years.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.63,0:20:54.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go on with your life.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.10,0:21:01.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Legs Benedict!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.94,0:21:09.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Say it-{\i1}bon{\i}, Pedro!\NWhy did you come back?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.24,0:21:18.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To this nightmarish island where your partner got killed\Nand 50 years of your life was taken away!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.25,0:21:26.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Straw Hats saved my home country\Nand I'm indebted to them!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.34,0:21:41.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On top of that,\NI believe they'll lead the world to the dawn one day!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.73,0:21:48.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pedro!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.90,0:21:56.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The dawn of the world will come before long!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.29,0:22:07.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In time, the Straw Hats will surpass you-{\i1}gara{\i} people\Nand change the world!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.34,0:22:12.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They can't do anything!\NWhere do you think you are-{\i1}bon{\i}?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.13,0:22:14.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the Whole Cake Island-{\i1}bon{\i}!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.72,0:22:17.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So what?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.22,0:22:20.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I believe in the Straw Hats.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.39,0:22:26.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I'm happy to spend\Nthe short remainder of my life...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.11,0:22:34.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...for them!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.32,0:22:36.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But don't get me wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.49,0:22:39.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not gonna die here!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.04,0:22:47.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They haven't met their goal on this island yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.56,0:23:08.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not gonna die now.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.69,0:23:16.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Cutting ties with his friends,\NSanji looks forward to marrying Pudding, his only hope.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.99,0:23:22.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}However, when a dark plot behind the wedding\Nand a stunning secret are revealed,{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.37,0:23:27.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}he stands in a daze all alone\Nas the cold rain pours down his back.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.29,0:23:31.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the next episode of One Piece!\N"Moist Cigarlette! The Night Before Sanji's Wedding!"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.25,0:23:39.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna be the King of the Pirates!\N
